com.lukeleber.scandroid.sae.j1979.util

Class CumulativePIDSupport

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lukeleber.scandroid.sae.j1979.util.CumulativePIDSupport

  • public class CumulativePIDSupport
extends java.lang.Object
    A CumulativePIDSupport is a form of PIDSupport that covers the entire support range; that is, from ID 0 to ID 255. This utility class is a convenience function for obtaining all supported PIDs/TIDs/OBDMIDs from the vehicle in a single statement.
